"tan, lo-fi (bit crushing), overdrive, or waveshape."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_audioeffectdistortion.rst:23
msgid ""
"By distorting the waveform the frequency content change, which will often"
" make the sound \"crunchy\" or \"abrasive\". For games, it can simulate "
"sound coming from some saturated device or speaker very efficiently."
